videos.description: Malik Monk catches the lob with one hand and throws down the alley-oop with one hand in the first half against Duquesne.
videos.headline: Monk finishes one-handed alley-oop with authority

videos.description: Isaiah Briscoe throws up the lob to Mychal Mulder who finishes the alley-oop in the first half against Duquesne.
videos.headline: Briscoe tosses the lob, Mulder gets up for the dunk
UK defense swarms on the fast break for a big time block
I. Briscoe makes it look easy as he weaves through defenders on the fast break lay up
M. Monk hammers down the one handed slam
E. Adebayo protecting the rim as he leaps up for the rejection
E. Adebayo jams in the put back dunk
Duquesne takes advantage of UK late with back to back steals and fast break finishes
